Have we met before?

261
00:25:04,300 --> 00:25:07,510
"Search for the Best Chef."

262
00:25:07,680 --> 00:25:09,809
"Thursdays at 6:30 on MBC."

263
00:25:09,810 --> 00:25:12,849
"The youngest female chef
