into a concrete pillar.

1016
01:53:20,100 --> 01:53:24,520
You're now
inside Lee Woo-jin's penthouse.

1017
01:53:25,150 --> 01:53:27,310
<i>It's a dreary night.</i>

1018
01:53:30,110 --> 01:53:33,069
<i>The sound of your footsteps
crossing to the window</i>

1019
01:53:33,070 --> 01:53:35,410
<i>fills the room.</i>

1020
01:53:49,050 --> 01:53:53,090
<i>When I ring my bell...</i>

1021
01:53:54,050 --> 01:53:57,430
<i>..you'll split into two people.</i>

1022
01:54:01,060 --> 01:54:04,940
<i>One person doesn't know
your secret.: Oh Dae-su.</i>

1023
01:54:05,690 --> 01:54:09,020
<i>The one who knows your secret
is the monster.</i>

1024
01:54:09,980 --> 01:54:12,439
<i>When I ring the bell again,</i>

1025
01:54:12,440 --> 01:54:16,030
<i>the monster will turn around
and start walking.</i>

1026
01:54:20,370 --> 01:54:26,369
<i>With each step,
he will age by one year.</i>

1027
01:54:26,370 --> 01:54:29,750
<i>When he reaches 70,
the monster will die.</i>

1028
01:54:29,840 --> 01:54:31,840
<i>There's no need to worry.</i>

1029
01:54:32,340 --> 01:54:35,550
<i>It will be a very peaceful death.</i>

1030
01:54:42,720 --> 01:54:44,730
<i>Now, good luck to you.</i>

1031
01:55:26,890 --> 01:55:29,440
What's going on?

1032
01:55:29,900 --> 01:55:32,440
Look at you.

1033
01:56:01,090 --> 01:56:03,220
Who were you with?

1034
01:56:58,650 --> 01:57:00,650
I love you...

1035
01:57:01,280 --> 01:57:03,030
..Dae-su..

